item.title: ![CDATA[Pentagon Kills LifeLog Project]]
item.description: ![CDATA[The Pentagon canceled its so-called LifeLog project, an ambitious effort to build a database tracking a person's entire existence. Run by Darpa, the Defense Department's research arm, LifeLog aimed to gather in a single place just about everything an individual says, sees or does: the phone calls made, the TV shows watched, the magazines read, [â€¦]]]
